 questioning findings from a\npseudoscientific e-Print. Overall, our work emphasizes the need to quickly and\neffectively validate non-peer-reviewed e-Prints that get substantial\npress/social media coverage to help mitigate wrongful interpretations of\nscientific outputs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 18:22:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2023 18:25:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2023 14:04:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-09"}
