ghting that model comparison and assessment should resemble the\ntrue predictive task. Our results also demonstrate that the proposed joint\nspecies distribution model can be used to simultaneously infer interspecific\ncorrelations in niche preference as well as mutual exclusive competition for\nspace and through that provide novel insight into ecological research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 18:28:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2022 11:28:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2023 14:16:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-06"}
