ular to the kagome plane. The latter\ninstability is partly contributed by the states at the Fermi surface and may be\nrelevant to the magnetic behavior of Co$_3$Sn$_2$S$_2$ near the Curie\ntemperature. Peculiarities of the half-metallic ferromagnetism in\nCo$_3$Sn$_2$S$_2$ are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 01:29:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-17"}
