ical values of $|W_{2}|/W_{1}$ are\ndetermined for the PS states, in which two ordered phases of the same type\n(i.e., two domains of the DCO or TCO phase) coexist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 09:25:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-05"}
