iz) rule, chain rule, and semigroup\nproperty. General FVC for orthogonal curvilinear coordinates, which includes\ngeneral fractional vector operators for the spherical and cylindrical\ncoordinates, is also proposed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 10:01:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-09"}
