pin of $0.47^{+0.10}_{-0.11}$,\nbut if their natal spins follow the observed HMXB spins, the average spinup\nmust be $<0.03$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 15:14:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Apr 2022 14:40:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-27"}
